{"tid":1659490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新水技 [水廉洗] 解鎖!","createTime":"2019-10-17T03:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T20:02:06.000Z","uid":39858,"like":17,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9859d31a8c7ebd11513cc6753802dfd8a3e211","tid":1659490,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/manlok.chan.7393/videos/395692908018499/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmanlok.chan.7393%2Fvideos%2F395692908018499%2F&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgDizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=933c7d20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/manlok.chan.7393/videos/395692908018499/</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">20/10 係理和非既日子 黑警會重兵係九龍 <br />\n勇武既巴打千拆唔好去同黑警硬碰 美國正審議香港人權與民主法案 畫面一定唔可能暴力<br />\n也不宜跟少數族裔開新戰線 之前黑警已經試過挑釁班穆斯林同我地開戰 好彩佢地唔成功<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港18區每區都有不同既巴士總站 影響好多班次 同市民<br />\n勇武巴打唔好去快閃出水廉洗呀 個畫面太溫馨太浪漫 美國佬好難唔接受ga</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/67yS65Q.jpg\" /><br />\n10 20 與岑同行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五行抗暴<br />\n水德為首<br />\n五大訢求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"56dc7cf743bc149a9e32de02516a1eae0a5d74c8","tid":1659490,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a99a42388ffd6394679270f06fa709b658c2115d","tid":1659490,"uid":252883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"亞巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1703ae6b194bbc127b4e9cb7e6428d15c51c8846","tid":1659490,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99a42388ffd6394679270f06fa709b658c2115d","tid":1659490,"uid":252883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s